data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.   Welcome to this charming four-bedroom, two-bathroom ranch-style home that's sure to capture your heart. Step inside and discover a beautifully updated interior, featuring stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, perfect for whipping up your favorite culinary delights. You'll appreciate the fresh new carpet and a full interior paint that exudes a clean and modern ambiance throughout the home. Convenience abounds with a spacious laundry room nestled in the hallway, complete with ample storage shelving for all your organizational needs. Each of the four bedrooms is equipped with ceiling fans for your comfort, and the primary bedroom is thoughtfully separated from the guest bedrooms, offering you privacy and a peaceful retreat. The open and flowing floor plan ensures a seamless connection between the kitchen and the inviting living room, perfect for entertaining guests. Step outside to the covered patio, where you can enjoy the tranquility of the fully fenced, grassy backyard. Whether you're hosting a barbecue, playing with pets, or simply savoring the outdoors, this space provides endless possibilities. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional ranch-style home your own - it's the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience. The refrigerator in the kitchen will be included with the sale of the home.
